4.4 How Execution Happens Technically

This is your architecture.

Option A — GitHub Actions (simplest for V3)
InfoGrid → triggers workflow_dispatch → runs job


Pros:

Easy

Free runners

Secure secrets

Perfect starting point

Option B — Self-hosted runners
InfoGrid → runner on client VM


Pros:

Private infra

More control

Enterprise friendly

Option C — Kubernetes Jobs
InfoGrid → creates k8s Job/Pod


Pros:

Scalable

Fast

Ideal for SaaS

This becomes your V4 architecture.
